701891f-a.title: Bronx: Tiffany Street - Fox Street
701891f-a.text:
Tiffany Street, west side, north from Fox Street. In the background
is visible the elevated trestle of the I.R.T. Lexington Ave. subway line,
on Westchester Ave.
1923.
Eeystone View Co., Inc., of New York.
